msgctxt "sn48.56:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 48 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 48 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn48.56:0.2"
msgid "6. Sūkarakhatavagga "
msgstr "6. The Boar’s Cave "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn48.56:0.3"
msgid "56. Patiṭṭhitasutta "
msgstr "56. Grounded "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.232, sc1
msgctxt "sn48.56:1.1"
msgid "“Ekadhamme patiṭṭhitassa, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno pañcindriyāni bhāvitāni honti subhāvitāni. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, when a mendicant is grounded in one thing the five faculties become developed, well developed. "

msgctxt "sn48.56:1.2"
msgid "Katamasmiṃ ekadhamme? "
msgstr "What one thing? "

msgctxt "sn48.56:1.3"
msgid "Appamāde. "
msgstr "Diligence. "

msgctxt "sn48.56:1.4"
msgid "Katamo ca bhikkhave, appamādo? "
msgstr "And what is diligence? "

# NOTE: At SN 22.48 the five khandha, including rupa are said to be sasava, which suggests that the term is similar to upadaniya, i.e. provocative of defilements.
msgctxt "sn48.56:1.5"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu cittaṃ rakkhati āsavesu ca sāsavesu ca dhammesu. "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant looks after their mind when it comes to defilements and things that stimulate defilements. "

msgctxt "sn48.56:1.6"
msgid "Tassa cittaṃ rakkhato āsavesu ca sāsavesu ca dhammesu saddhindriyampi bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchati. "
msgstr "As they do so the faculties of faith, "

msgctxt "sn48.56:1.7"
msgid "Vīriyindriyampi bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchati. "
msgstr "energy, "

msgctxt "sn48.56:1.8"
msgid "Satindriyampi bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchati. "
msgstr "mindfulness, "

msgctxt "sn48.56:1.9"
msgid "Samādhindriyampi bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchati. "
msgstr "immersion, "

msgctxt "sn48.56:1.10"
msgid "Paññindriyampi bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchati. "
msgstr "and wisdom are fully developed. "

msgctxt "sn48.56:1.11"
msgid "Evampi kho, bhikkhave, ekadhamme patiṭṭhitassa bhikkhuno pañcindriyāni bhāvitāni honti subhāvitānī”ti. "
msgstr "That’s how when a mendicant is grounded in one thing the five faculties become developed, well developed.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn48.56:1.12"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ. "
msgstr ""

